Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}Reunions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:13.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}Usually a time for former classmates to meet once more,\Nand be surprised at how they’ve each changed since parting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:17.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}But sometimes, they can become\Nthe scene of cases nobody could expect...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.79,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We won’t give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.67,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:28.17,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A strange and impossible murder\Namong judo buddies from university!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:29.84,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.71,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:34.47,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
