Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:24.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0002,,Why won’t you take us to your reunion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0002,,What do you mean why? It’s my reunion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0002,,You took me to the one five years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:33.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0002,,But we can’t let the office close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:36.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if something big happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But with you on vacation, the office would be closed no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to go to the hot spring, too! Right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:49.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was going to treat you to a fancy meal instead of taking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we’ll pass on the meal and take the hot spring trip instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Domestic flights are even more expensive than international ones lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t wanna pay for three stinking people! Put yourself in my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the truth comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He just robbed the bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You’re not getting away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Stay back or I’ll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:35.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! You caught a bank robber, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like taking candy from a baby
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when the great detective Kogoro Mouri is on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:47.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! How did you make that brick do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I thought he was going to shoot you,\Nso I kicked it without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and it just happened to hit the robber’s gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you saved his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you’re obligated to take the person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:07.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who saved your life to the hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’ll come as Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}’s guardian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:26.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My company’s right nearby. I came to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re Horikoshi-{\i1}san{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that you, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:31.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to the reunion at the hot spring again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who said—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t wait to see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yumi! Ran’s not—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:52.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Kogoro Mouri-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:03.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you’re not going to take the gun the robber had?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:13.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s strange. I’m almost certain that his gun landed over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:19.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me someone on this street ran off with it during all the commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! T-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to tell HQ and get it back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We only looked away for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who could’ve taken it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Eating while on a trip is the best thing ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:43.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to take that little brat to the reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the problem? You took me to the one five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:58.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were little at the time, so I couldn’t leave you at home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:04.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn’t be able to attend this reunion if Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} hadn’t saved your life, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:10.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could’ve caught that guy easy enough without the kid’s help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did they ever find that missing gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:19.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what’s the deal? The police haven’t announced anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:23.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the police are investigating really hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it hasn’t been used in any other crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and they don’t seem to have any leads, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The gun was a Smith and Wesson M439.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:35.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That robber doesn’t know much about guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He paid a lot of money for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he didn’t know the difference between a real gun and a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}“Hot Spring Resort — Benkei”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is good to see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:10.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:13.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the first time since our last reunion five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:18.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...that everyone from the Beika University Judo Club has been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:22.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure brings back memories of all those days of intense practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:27.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’re you to talk?\NYou rarely ever came to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:31.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right! You constantly ditched practice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because you thought geniuses didn’t need to train! Right, Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:38.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you were the only one who never won a single match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:40.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was because—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}knew{\i0} it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lying whenever you boasted that you were invincible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,during your university days, weren’t you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}! It’s good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into her a while ago... She really has grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’ve you been this entire time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The open-air bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The open-air bath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a mixed-gender bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s alright, there was nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you two took a bath together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to get Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} to go,\Nhe was so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:24.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that sure was fun, scrubbing each other’s back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A nosebleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bath must’ve rushed the blood to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure he’s not over-excited\Nfrom seeing you naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:36.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he’s not! He’s still a kid, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I am so dead if she finds out who I really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:44.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, so this is the boy Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0} is taking care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:53.47,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,High School Gym Teacher\NYukio Ayashiro (38)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:52.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Beika University’s judo ace, Ayashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meetcha, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:59.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Model Shop Owner\NJun Omura (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Jun Omura, our judo club’s biggest risk-taker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was our so-called “point-getter”!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:04.35,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Cosmetic Company Employee\NYumi Horikoshi (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:04.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Yumi Horikoshi, the beautiful manager of the judo club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name used to be Noriko Kimoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:12.82,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Housewife\NNoriko Ayashiro (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I also was the manager and idol of the judo club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I’m this man’s wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:19.28,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiba Prefectural Police Detective\NKazushi Nakamichi (38)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:17.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Nakamichi. I was captain and central pillar of the team!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a police detective in Chiba prefecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:23.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, unlike this guy, I haven’t quit my job halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Every one of them is a judo ace or idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:38.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And as you all know, I’m the great detective and judo master once called “Beika’s Sanshiro”—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that our old university album?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I brought it so we could all look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Can’t you hear people out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is from when we won second place at the city tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re all so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:08.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamichi and Yumi were an item back then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:12.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. We cried together back then, didn’t we, Omura?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:13.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were definitely the judo club’s Madonna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough. You’re my husband now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are the two of you still—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:30.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be silly! I dumped this clod a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, he’s already chosen someone to marry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re getting married, Nakamichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:44.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I had hoped to formally announce it to you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the ceremony’s going to be sometime this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss’s daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We met six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll introduce her to you guys sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:59.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, the former Madonna is still a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:04.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I might lose my job\Nbecause of the bad economy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:07.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish I were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! I just wanted to see how you would react!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t scare us like that, Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:21.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means me and Omura-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nare the only unmarried ones left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:30.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re so stupid! It was a joke!\NDon’t take it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:39.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Isn’t this picture from when\Nwe came here five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I’m in the picture too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:46.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We took this picture in the ping-pong room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I stuck this photo in here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! What do you say\Nwe play some ping-pong now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:58.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we’re supposed to watch\Nthe fireworks in the evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:01.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry. The fireworks start at 6:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have over three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we end before 6:00, we’ll make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:06.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m tired for some reason.\NI’ll be resting in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s still the same as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She does everything at her own pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She just doesn’t want people pulling her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let’s play some ping-pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs and ping-pong go perfect together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven’t been this raring to go for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:30.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a gym instructor, I can’t afford to lose to the lot of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\a6}“Ping-Pong Room”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Get ready for another!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re up next, so hurry on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:45.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:50.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t you win an individual award\Nat a national championship before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:54.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, only once, when I was in my third year at university.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:59.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you must’ve been the best\Nmember of the club, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there was a guy who was much better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never beat him even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You had someone that good in your club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:11.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him too, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}.\NHe’s even staying at this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Curveballs aren’t fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? That was pretty fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Yukio-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heads up, Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re so silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:43.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, how long are you two\Ngoing to play so stupidly like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn’t it time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! It’s already past 6:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:54.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! We have to hurry! The place’ll be crowded!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let’s hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:01.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll return the rackets and stuff.\NYou go find us a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We forgot to wake up Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about her. It’s about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure someone’s woken her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if we all forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go make sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. They really should’ve left her alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to wake her up right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 201. This is her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks have started already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m coming in, Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamichi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t you go on ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to wake up Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’d better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets real grouchy whenever\Nsomebody wakes her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Nakamichi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked up a sweat playing\Nping-pong, so I took a quick bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s when I heard you two running...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:27.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange, since we’re\Nthe only ones staying at this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you still doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask you the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:36.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were washing off your sweat too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:40.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. But I was in the public bath unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:45.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}! It was definitely\Nbest that you didn’t wake Yumi up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s really grouchy when she wakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:52.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She’ll still be mad we didn’t wake her up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is crowded! Don’t let go of my hand, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Everyone was just with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:14.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They got separated from us in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I’ll look around for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Omura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like a restless kind of guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:29.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Omura went through\Nthe trouble to find a spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but not a single one of you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:31.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:35.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Omura went to look for\Nyou but never came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as is often the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot where our spot was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some sake and forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:45.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys do things your own way far too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}’s still not up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:49.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Yeah, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be awake by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:57.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be pouting because\Nshe missed the fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You’re all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:06.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we all go and\Nwake up the judo club’s Madonna?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yumi! It’s dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you still asleep? I’m turning the light on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:32.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody but me and Mouri are to come in here, since we’re detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Call the police immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:41.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:42.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bullet hole in her temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun in her right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:59.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Isn’t that the gun the bank robber had!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:05.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The gun is a Smith and Wesson M439!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the barrel looks like it’s\Nbeen struck by something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:12.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s more, Yumi was at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.40,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.69,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.40,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.82,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My company’s right nearby. I came to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:28.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So Yumi picked up the gun because she\Nhad intended to use it from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:32.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means she had planned\Nto commit suicide at our reunion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it’s too early to make any conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s wait until the police get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, good call...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Two hours until the police get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They said the streets are crowded\Nbecause of the festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We can’t wait two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice! We’ll have\Nto do the autopsy ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:09.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have a camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us borrow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go get it from my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:21.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would’ve thought we would\Nbe giving Yumi an autopsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All finished here, Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her toes are beginning to stiffen too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a bit of time has passed since she died...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we check for death spots as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:48.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But given the amount of blood that\Nshe’s lost, she might not have any...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:52.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she’s not wearing anything underneath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not all that’s strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, she’s wearing a large yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was wearing a small one\Nwhen she was in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:07.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the index finger of the\Nhand that’s holding the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,isn’t on the trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:12.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the strangest thing is that this bullet wound—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little—!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re always getting in the\Nway of my investigations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:20.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find anything out, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the state of her rigor mortis,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:28.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi died over seven hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:33.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven hours ago... Which means around 3:00 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:36.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s when we were in the\Nping-pong room, after she left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:40.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Most likely she returned to her room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and shot herself in the head\Nwith a gun she had hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there’s no question it was a suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would she kill herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she did say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.98,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I really wish I were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She really must’ve been thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:59.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how did Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0} shoot herself in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:28.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:29.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ask strange questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:31.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:32.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:36.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She put the gun up to her head like so and—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Mouri! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:44.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Nakamichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:46.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally when someone\Ncommits suicide with a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:49.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they stick the barrel against their head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:49.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:54.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then her bullet wound is missing something vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:59.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You’re right! Burn marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:05.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you shoot a gun, a stream\Nof hot air accompanies the bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:08.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you shoot with the gun against your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:10.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have to leave burn marks behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:13.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that there are none here means...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:16.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...t-that someone else shot her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:21.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone shot her and then tried\Nto make it look like a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:24.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone in this inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:47.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What are you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:49.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:51.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw who? The killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:56.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the supposedly-dead\NYumi in a window upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.99,0:24:00.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to catch whoever killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:04.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I’ve finally figured out the trick the killer used!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You were the one who killed Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:14.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:19.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan’s Hint: Ping-Pong
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:24.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.89,0:24:24.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:22.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You had a bath with Ran-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:23.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My nosebleed was twice as big as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:24.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You perverted brat.
